ed="T" n="0887b18"/><persName key="A013808">釋義莊</persName>，姓<name>張氏</name>，<placeName key="PL000000024155">滑臺</placeName>人也。當免懷之日<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2323"/>，及<lb
ed="T" n="0887b19"/>就傅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2324"/>之秋，神彩克明，塵機頓去。乃於本府<placeName key="PL000000024133">開<lb
ed="T" n="0887b20"/>元寺</placeName>歸善財之列<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2325"/>，從升戒德。因樂遊方，始<lb
ed="T" n="0887b21"/>於<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛邑</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0887sgsz7"/>采<anchor xml:id="end0887sgsz7"/>聽《法華》，見識過人，闡揚訓物，眾<lb
ed="T" n="0887b22"/>請居<placeName key="PL000000049321">九曜院</placeName><ptr target="#n3501"/>焉。匪虧法食，用濟往來。慈以<lb
ed="T" n="0887b23"/>利生，始末無<anchor xml:id="beg0887sgsz8"/>間<anchor xml:id="end0887sgsz8"/>。<date notBefore-iso="+0960-02-09" key="j20717322072081" notAfter-iso="+0961-01-23"><name>建隆</name>初</date>左散騎常侍<persName key="A042580">申<roleName>公</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n2050"/>奏<lb
ed="T" n="0887b24"/>賜紫衣<ptr target="#n3502"/>，稟學<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2326"/>僧尼三十餘員。<persName key="A013808">莊</persName>性敦勤，進講<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2327"/><lb
ed="T" n="0887b25"/>外兢兢<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2328"/>五十年<anchor xml:id="beg0887sgsz9"/>間<anchor xml:id="end0887sgsz9"/>，二時<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1114"/><anchor xml:id="beg0887sgsz11"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0887sgsz11"/>懺，至老不替<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g522"/>。於<lb
ed="T" n="0887b26"/><date notBefore-iso="+0978-09-10" key="j20785202078549" notAfter-iso="+0978-10-09"><name>太平興國</name>戊寅年八月</date>奄終，俗壽七十八，僧<lb
ed="T" n="0887b27"/>臘五十九。<date notBefore-iso="+0979-03-06" key="j20786972078726" notAfter-iso="+0979-04-04">明年二月</date>，遷塔于<placeName key="PL000000023660"><placeName>龍門</placeName><placeName>菩提寺</placeName></placeName>西<lb
ed="T" n="0887b28"/>焉。</p>
